### Configure Transformers.js Model Caching in Node.js

Source: https://github.com/huggingface/transformers.js/blob/main/docs/source/tutorials/node.md

This JavaScript snippet illustrates how to configure the cache directory for Transformers.js models. By setting `env.cacheDir`, you can specify a custom location on the file system where downloaded model files will be stored, improving subsequent loading times.

```javascript
env.cacheDir = './.cache';

```

