### Convert and Quantize Model to ONNX using Transformers.js Script

Source: https://github.com/huggingface/transformers.js/blob/main/README.md

This script converts and optionally quantizes a specified model to the ONNX format. It requires Python and the transformers.js package. The input is a model ID, and the output is a set of ONNX files saved locally.

```bash
python -m scripts.convert --quantize --model_id <model_name_or_path>
```

```bash
python -m scripts.convert --quantize --model_id bert-base-uncased
```

