### Load Gated Model Tokenizer (JavaScript)

Source: https://github.com/huggingface/transformers.js/blob/main/docs/source/guides/private.md

This JavaScript code snippet demonstrates how to load a tokenizer for a gated Hugging Face model using the Transformers.js library. It requires the HF_TOKEN environment variable to be set for authentication. The output is the encoded representation of the input text.

```javascript
import { AutoTokenizer } from '@huggingface/transformers';

// Load tokenizer for a gated repository.
const tokenizer = await AutoTokenizer.from_pretrained('meta-llama/Llama-2-7b-hf');

// Encode text.
const text = 'Hello world!';
const encoded = tokenizer.encode(text);
console.log(encoded);
```

