### Transformers.js Pipeline API - Custom Model

Source: https://context7.com/huggingface/transformers.js/llms.txt

Shows how to use a specific, custom model from the Hugging Face Hub for a task. This example loads a model specialized for 5-star review sentiment analysis.

```javascript
import { pipeline } from '@huggingface/transformers';

// Use a custom model for 5-star review sentiment
const reviewer = await pipeline(
    'sentiment-analysis',
    'Xenova/bert-base-multilingual-uncased-sentiment'
);

const result = await reviewer('The Shawshank Redemption is a true masterpiece of cinema.');
console.log(result);
// Output: [{label: '5 stars', score: 0.8167929649353027}]
```
